sources.title: Boost | Full Action Crime Movie
sources.description:
Boost - Hakeem and A-Mac are like brothers. Together they face immigrant life in Montreal, while 'spotting' cars after school. Boost gives us a glimpse into the awkward adventures of teenage boyhood, then the jolt, when that innocence ends abruptly.
2016.  Stars: Nabil Rajo, Jahmil French, Ntare Guma Mbaho Mwine
